{"id":"sinim-the-land-of","term":"Sinim, The land of","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 49:12\">Isa. 49:12</a>), supposed by some to mean China, but more probably Phoenicia (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 10:17\">Gen. 10:17</a>) is intended.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Isaiah 49:12","Genesis 10:17"]}